  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large Dutch oven over medium heat. Add onion and cook until softened, about 8 minutes.",
    "Stir in garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add gherkin relish, cumin, coriander, cinnamon, cayenne pepper, salt, and black pepper. Cook for 2 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Add prunes and cook for 2 minutes, stirring to combine.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer, uncovered, for 20 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Stir in parsley and adjust seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve over couscous or crusty bread"
